The paper deals with algorithms for edge coloring multigraphs, which is a topic in discrete mathematics (cs.DM). The use of the probabilistic method and the Lopsided Lovasz Local Lemma suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the sub-categories of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), computational complexity (cs.CC), graph theory (cs.GT), and information theory (cs.IT).
